## Summary: Milestone: Project Artifact Persistence

### Changes Implemented
- `apps/server/src/services/project-artifact-service.ts` — Already existed with a complete implementation in this branch:
  - `saveArtifact(projectPath, slug, type, content)` — writes artifact to `.automaker/projects/{slug}/artifacts/{type}/{id}.json` and updates the index file
  - `listArtifacts(projectPath, slug, type?)` — returns index entries, with optional type filter
  - `getArtifact(projectPath, slug, artifactId)` — returns artifact content; throws `'Artifact not found'` for unknown IDs
  - Singleton export `projectArtifactService`
- All four required types (`ArtifactType`, `ArtifactIndexEntry`, `ArtifactIndex`, `ProjectArtifact`) were already present in `libs/types/src/project.ts`
- `apps/server/src/services/ceremony-service.ts` already imports `projectArtifactService` and calls `saveArtifact` for both `milestone_retro` and `project_retro` ceremony completions
